title: AOMEI Backupper 1.6 [Windows 7, 8 and Server 2008 R2, 2012]
description:
AOMEI Backupper 1.6

AOMEI Backupper - Especially Designed for Windows 7, 8 and Server 2008 R2, 2012

   System Backup, Disk/Partition Backup, Volume Backup

   Disk Clone, Partition Clone

   Create Windows PE Bootable Media without installing Windows AIK

   

License :Freeware

Platform :Windows 7, 8 and Server 2008 R2, 2012

Size :20MB

   

Main Features:

   System Backup

   Disk Backup

   Partition Backup

   Schedule Backup

   System Restore

   Disk/Partition Restore

   Selective File Restore

   Clone Disk

   Clone Partition

Additional Features:

   Image File Checker and Explorer

   Create Bootable Rescue Media

   Incremental & Differential Backups

   Encryption and Compression

   Comment Backups and Splitting Backups

   NAS Supported

   GPT & UEFI Boot Supported

   Dynamic Volumes Supported

Work Environment:

   Operating System: Windows 8, 7 and Server 2008 R2, 2012 (32/64-bit).

   Storage Devices: Support almost all storage devices recognized by Windows, such as fixed hard disk drive (HDD), external USB HDD, Solid-State Drive (SSD), Flash Drive, USB 3.0 drive, Hardware RAID, Network-Attached Storage (NAS).

   Disk Style: Support MBR and GPT disk styles, working with EFI/UEFI boot smoothly, dynamic volumes supported.
